# Allowlist ONLY these two hosts. One host per line, matched as an FQDN
# (see tinyproxy.conf: FilterExtended On).
# 1. The upstream Metro Train GTFS-Realtime gateway (2a).
^api\.opendata\.transport\.vic\.gov\.au$
# 2. The external dead-man's-switch ping target (2b) — deliberate, narrow
# widening confirmed by Ronnie 2026-07-21, not the default upstream host.
^hc-ping\.com$
